room_title: Escape room "Orion" by The Hidden Escape in Atlanta
room_address: 6867 S. Sweetwater Rd. Unit A Lithia Springs, GA 30122
room_description: Professor Eisenstein has dedicated his life to studying the skies and journeying across the seas in a search for hidden treasures. However, as he is getting older and weaker from his past adventures, he is needing an apprentice to accompany him and continue his legacy. He’s recruited you to join him… but first, you have to pass his test. Do you have what it takes?
